	PARPACK/UTIL/MPI/Makefile
	PARPACK/UTIL/BLACS/Makefile
	PARPACK/EXAMPLES/MPI/Makefile
	PARPACK/TESTS/MPI/Makefile
	PARPACK/EXAMPLES/BLACS/Makefile
	])
